import * as React from 'react';
import AppBar from '@mui/material/AppBar';
import Box from '@mui/material/Box';
import Toolbar from '@mui/material/Toolbar';
import IconButton from '@mui/material/IconButton';
import Typography from '@mui/material/Typography';
import MenuIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Menu';
import Container from '@mui/material/Container';
import OrderButton from '../ProductScreen/OrderButton/OrderButton';

const Navbar = () => {
  return (
    <AppBar position="static" sx={{"backgroundColor":"white"}}>
      <Container style={{"background":"white","color":"black"}}>
        <Box sx={{ flexGrow: 1, display: { xs: 'none', md: 'flex'} }} style={{"marginTop":"30px"}}>
        <Typography
            variant="p"
            noWrap
            component="a"
            href=""
            sx={{
              mr: 2,
              display: { xs: 'flex'},
              flexGrow: 1,
              fontWeight:500,
              fontSize:'large',
              color: 'inherit',
              textDecoration: 'none',
            }}
          >
            Laptops
          </Typography>
          <Typography
            variant="p"
            noWrap
            component="a"
            href=""
            sx={{
              mr: 2,
              display: { xs: 'flex'},
              flexGrow: 1,
              fontWeight:500,
              fontSize:'large',
              color: 'inherit',
              textDecoration: 'none',
            }}
          >
            Desktop PCs
          </Typography>
          <Typography
            variant="p"
            noWrap
            component="a"
            href=""
            sx={{
              mr: 2,
              display: { xs: 'flex'},
              flexGrow: 1,
              fontWeight:500,
              fontSize:'large',
              color: 'inherit',
              textDecoration: 'none',
            }}
          >
            Networking Devices
          </Typography>
          <Typography
            variant="p"
            noWrap
            component="a"
            href=""
            sx={{
              mr: 2,
              display: { xs: 'flex'},
              flexGrow: 1,
              fontWeight:500,
              fontSize:'large',
              color: 'inherit',
              textDecoration: 'none',
            }}
          >
            Printer Scanner
          </Typography>
          <Typography
            variant="p"
            noWrap
            component="a"
            href=""
            sx={{
              mr: 2,
              display: { xs: 'flex'},
              flexGrow: 1,
              fontWeight:500,
              fontSize:'large',
              color: 'inherit',
              textDecoration: 'none',
            }}
          >
            PC Parts
          </Typography>
          <Typography
            variant="p"
            noWrap
            component="a"
            href=""
            sx={{
              mr: 2,
              display: { xs: 'flex'},
              flexGrow: 1,
              fontWeight:500,
              fontSize:'large',
              color: 'inherit',
              textDecoration: 'none',
            }}
          >
            All Other Products
          </Typography>
          <Typography
            variant="p"
            noWrap
            component="a"
            href=""
            sx={{
              mr: 2,
              display: { xs: 'flex'},
              flexGrow: 1,
              fontWeight:500,
              fontSize:'large',
              color: 'inherit',
              textDecoration: 'none',
            }}
          >
            Repairs
          </Typography>
        </Box>
        <Box sx={{ flexGrow: 1, display: { xs: 'none', md: 'flex'} }}>
          <OrderButton/>
        </Box>
        <Toolbar disableGutters sx={{flexGrow:1, display:{xs:"block",md:'none',float:"right"}}} style={{"boxShadow":"revert"}}>
          {/* <Box sx={{ flexGrow: 1, display: { xs: 'flex', md: 'none', float:"right" } }}> */}
            <IconButton
              size="large"
              aria-label="account of current user"
              aria-controls="menu-appbar"
              aria-haspopup="true"
              color="inherit"
            >
              <MenuIcon />
            </IconButton>
          {/* </Box> */}
        </Toolbar>
      </Container>
    </AppBar>
  );
};
export default Navbar;
